# Build outputs
dist/
build/
out/
target/
*.o
*.so
*.dylib
*.exe
*.dll

# Stray go-build output at the repo root, e.g. `go build ./zarlcode/cmd` → ./cmd
# and `go build ./examples/hnupvote` → ./hnupvote. The real install target is
# ~/.local/bin (see Taskfile.yml); these root copies are accidental.
/cmd
/hnupvote
# Likewise `cd zarlcode && go build ./cmd` → ./zarlcode/zarlcode.
/zarlcode/zarlcode
# `go build -o bin/zarlcode` → a ~68MB binary; never track build artifacts.
/bin/

